title: Kendall Jenner Learns to Twerk in Balmain x H&M Behind the Scenes - Watch Now!
text: Kendall Jenner learns to twerk and get down in this brand new behind-the-scenes video from her Balmain x H&M collection campaign. The 19-year-old model is joined in the video by Balmain‘s Creative Director Olivier Rousteing and a troupe of professional dancers.
